claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A two‐year CONSORT flow diagram showing enrollment, randomization, and follow‐up of participants in four vaccine arms (ccIIV4, RIV4, Fluzone IIV4, FluARIX IIV4) in Year 1 and re‐randomization in Year 2. does not support the claim because the figure only presents participant allocation and study flow; it contains no data or statements about antigenic match with WHO‐ or FDA‐selected strains. Note: None.
